Name: Telium
AboutMe:
Developer and consultant for Telium. In addition to asking questions, we try to answer questions relating to Telematics and Telephony.

Please be aware that Telium is a vendor of Telematics and Telephony software. Opinions expressed on Stack Exchange represent the views of employees and may reflect an understanding of and bias for Telium products. (i.e. yes our views may be biased - but we try hard to keep opinions neutral!).

If you have a question about a Telium product we prefer not to answer on stack exchange - please email us at info@telium.ca We are happy to answer your questions regarding Telium products and services.
